      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This car is in good condition and has been well-cared for, making it a reliable and stylish choice for its next owner. It runs smoothly and looks great, offering a wonderful balance of quality and value for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle they can count on!",
