    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a serious restoration project or a source for spare parts. It currently has significant mechanical issues that prevent it from being a reliable daily driver, including a failing transmission and engine leaks. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust on the frame and several body panels, while the interior requires a complete overhaul due to torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please approach this purchase with the understanding that it will require substantial investment to become roadworthy again.",
